platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: At a glance, hocus doesnt look very complicated. You swipe to move a red cube along a latticework of plain grey beams. But dont let the minimalist visuals fool youthe games intelligent, abstract puzzles force you to look at things in a new way, like a cubist translation of Monument Valley. As you progress, the levels quickly get complex. But the peaceful music and crisp design make spending time in its world a richly rewarding experience.
